<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-7 offset-md-1 mt-3 pt-3 myBackground">

    <h1>Thank You!</h1>

    <% if @donation.frequency == 'Monthly' %>
      <h4>Thank you for your monthy donation of <strong><%= number_to_currency(@donation.amount) %></strong></h4>

      <p>Thank you for choosing to support Operation Paws for Homes each month.
      Monthly donations like yours provide a stable source of funding for medical care, food, transport and so much more.
      To make changes to your monthly donation in the future, please contact us at <a href='mailto:donate@ophrescue.org'>donate@ophrescue.org</a></p>
    <% else %>
      <h4>Your donation of <strong><%= number_to_currency(@donation.amount) %></strong> has been received.</h4>

      <p>Thank you for your thoughtful donation to Operation Paws for Homes! You make it possible for us to save dogs every single day.
      Your donations help us provide vaccinations, food, transportation, heartworm medicines, spaying and neutering, and so much more.
      We also depend on donations like yours for dogs suffering from severe neglect that require extra attention.</p>
    <% end %>

    <p>Did you know that many corporations offer employee giving programs where they match donations to Operation Paws for Homes? Check with your employer today to see if they provide matching gifts!</p>

    <h4>Looking for other ways you can help? It takes a village!</h4>

    <p><strong>Your time</strong> - Regardless of where you live or how much free time you have, there are ways you can volunteer. Visit our <a href="/get-involved">Get Involved</a> page to learn more.</p>
    <p><strong>Your Vehicle</strong> - Operation Paws for Homes has partnered with the Melwood Foundation to accept vehicle donations. For information on how to donate your vehicle to us call 1-877-MEL-WOOD</p>
    <p><strong>Shopping</strong> - Did you know you can shop online and support OPH at the same time? Learn more at <a href="/other-ways-to-give">Other Ways to Give</a></p>
    <p>Above all, thank you for choosing to donate to the OPH Rescue!</p>

      <ul class="list-unstyled">
        <li>Donor Name: <%= @donation.name %></li>
        <li>Donation Date: <%= @donation.created_at.strftime('%m/%d/%y') %> </li>
        <li>Donation Amount: <%= number_to_currency(@donation.amount) %></li>
      </ul>

